      <title>纳格尔称欧洲央行不应将利率降至中性水平以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-shouldn-t-cut-interest-rates-below-neutral-nagel-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员约阿希姆·纳格尔表示，欧洲央行可以逐步降低借贷成本至不再限制经济活动的水平，但不应降幅过大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/ecb-shouldn-t-cut-interest-rates-below-neutral-nagel-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 17:10:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
