      <title>HPS 向贝莱德出售后提供激励措施以留住员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hps-offers-incentives-to-retain-staff-after-sale-to-blackrock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博新闻看到的一封投资者信显示，HPS Investment Partners 正在向员工提供五年内归属的激励措施，以鼓励他们在被贝莱德收购后继续留任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/hps-offers-incentives-to-retain-staff-after-sale-to-blackrock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 16:49:46 GMT</pubDate>
